Edicy,is,a,cloud,based,service,for,building,and,hosting,multilingual,websites,and,managing,their,content,It,is,optimized,for,both,desktop,and,mobile,viewing,provides,built,in,SEO,and,comes,with,customizable,themes,The,Edicy,Site,API,allows,users,to,access,public,Edicy,site,contents,through,a,JSON,based,API,This,API,is,read,only,and,can,be,used,to,retrieve,articles,comments,and,other,page,elements